paragraphs.title: Creating a pair RDD with key/value
paragraphs.text:
%livy.pyspark

key_value_power = csv_car_data.map(lambda x: (x[0],float(x[6]))) 
power_by_key = key_value_power.reduceByKey(lambda x, y: x + y)
power_by_key.collect()

paragraphs.title: Average By Key
paragraphs.text:
%livy.pyspark

sum_counts = key_value_power.combineByKey(
    (lambda value: (value,1)), 
    (lambda x, value: (x[0]+value,x[1]+1)),
    (lambda x, y: (x[0]+y[0],x[1]+y[1])) 
)

average_by_key = sum_counts.map(lambda (label, (value_sum, count)): (label, value_sum / count))

print("{0}".format(average_by_key.collectAsMap()))
